@node arexx AREXX
                        Befor usin arexx

Rexx  was developed in the early 70 on UNIX Computers, to make it
easyer to remote controll programms.

              from Rexx AREXX (AmigaREXX) was born

To use AREXX on your Amiga, the rexxmast programm must run in the
back.   Users of Kickstart 2.x have already the rexxmast programm
on the Workbench.  1.3 user must bye the AREXX programms first.
@endnode

@node port AREXXPORT
                         The Arexxport

to  make  it  sure,  that the arexx commands reach the Framemachine
software, you have to put two lines in fornt of them:

address "Framemachine"  <---- Case sensetive!!!!!!
options results

In RESULT (yes without s) is the answer of the software.
@endnode

